					<witness xml:id="Translation">The Dream of Gong Yu</witness>
				</listWit>
			</div>
		</front>
		<body>
			<head>
				<title>
					<app>
						<lem wit="#Transcription">龔輿夢</lem>
						<rdg wit="#Translation">The Dream of Gong Yu</rdg>
					</app>
				</title>
			</head>
			<div n="1">
				<p>
					<app>
						<lem wit="#Transcription">
							<s>潭州士人龔輿,</s>
						</lem>
						<rdg wit="#Translation">
							<s>There is a literatus from Tanzhou named Gong Yu.</s>
						</rdg>
					</app>
					<app>
						<lem wit="#Transcription">
							<s>乾道四年冬,</s>
						</lem>
						<rdg wit="#Translation">
							<s>In the winter of the fourth year of the Dao Qian reign,</s>
						</rdg>
					</app>
					<app>
						<lem wit="#Transcription">
							<s>與鄉里六七人偕赴省試.</s>
						</lem>
						<rdg wit="#Translation">
							<s>he went together with six or seven people from his hometown to participate in the provincial exam.</s>
						</rdg>
					</app>
					<app>
						<lem wit="#Transcription">
							<s>過宜春,</s>
						</lem>
						<rdg wit="#Translation">
							<s>When they passed by Yi Chun,</s>
						</rdg>
					</app>
					<app>
						<lem wit="#Transcription">
							<s>謁仰山廟祈夢.</s>
						</lem>
						<rdg wit="#Translation">
							<s> they paid respects to the Yangshan Monastery and prayed for dreams.</s>
						</rdg>
					</app>
					<app>
						<lem wit="#Transcription">
							<s>輿夢至官府, 見柱上掲紙一片,</s>
						</lem>
						<rdg wit="#Translation">
							<s>Gong Yu dreamt he went into the government house and saw a piece of paper on the pillar of the house.</s>
						</rdg>
					</app>
					<app>
						<lem wit="#Transcription">
							<s>書[龔輿不得]四字,</s>
						</lem>
						<rdg wit="#Translation">
							<s>On the paper the four characters “Gong Yu Bu De” 
								<note type="critical" anchored="true">Meaning, “Gong Yu will not get it”
								</note>
								were written.</s>
							</rdg>
						</app>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">
								<s>而[不]字上下稍不聨接.</s>
							</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation">
								<s>But the upper part and the lower part of the character “Ge” were not connected.</s>
							</rdg>
						</app>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">
								<s>既覺, 殊不樂, 自意必下第.</s>
							</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation">
								<s>When Gong Yu woke up, he was rather unhappy and thought he would fail the exam.</s>
							</rdg>
						</app>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">
								<s>及春榜至, 輿中選, 餘人盡黜,</s>
							</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation">
								<s>When the results came out in the spring, (it turns out) Gong Yu was selected and the rest of his group were all rejected.</s>
							</rdg>
						</app>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">
								<s>始以語人, 謂夢不驗.</s>
							</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation">
								<s>Gong Yu then began to tell people, saying the dream was not accurate.</s>
							</rdg>
						</app>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">
								<s>好事者曰: “不字斷續如此, 乃一个也. 神言龔輿一个得耳, 豈不昭然?”</s>
							</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation">
								<s>The acquaintances said: “When the character ‘Ge’ were disconnected like this, it should be read as two characters ‘Yi Ge.’ The deity said only Gong Yu himself could get it, isn’t this obvious?”</s>
							</rdg>
						</app>
					</p>
				</div>
